Product Description

UGREEN HDMI Cable Extender HDMI Female to Female Coupler Support 4K 3D HDR Pass Through for HDMI Cable Extension

4K Female to Female HDMI Extension Coupler

UGREEN High Speed HDMI female to female adapter could convert a HDMI male into HDMI female interface, and extend your HDMI devices by connecting two short HDMI cables together.The gold-plated connectors that resist corrosion while offering optimum signal transfer.

Audio Video Sync

HDMI Adapter supports audio and video synchronization, no need for external speakers, easy to enjoy audio-visual feast.

Specification

  1. Connectors: HDMI Female(Type A) x2
  2. Convert an HDMI male interface into HDMI female
  3. Extend your HDMI devices by connecting 2pcs HDMI male to male cables together
  4. With gold-plated connectors that resist corrosion while offering optimum signal transfer

      Cliff G.
      5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for use with Fire TV 4K Stick
      Reviewed in the United States on November 17, 2018
      Verified Purchase
      This adapter allows the use of a Fire TV Stick (any generation or other brand dongle) with a proper length M-M HDMI cable, to allow advantageous placement for the best WiFi reception. Having the Stick plugged in behind the TV is a terrible location for strong WiFi reception, especially if using 5G. This also applies if you have a HT receiver where all the devices plug into HDMI ports on it. Remember, you are placing a 'radio transceiver' (the Stick) behind a slab of metal. How is that going to help getting solid reception? It won't. I have a Denon HT receiver that manages all of my HDMI devices, and I use a single HDMI cable from it to the Sony 4K TV. Get yourself a quality M-M HDMI cable (3-6') and one of these F-F HDMI Couplers to locate the TV Stick in the clear - NOT on top of (will distort reception) or behind (will block/reduce reception) a chunk of metal. Everything else being equal, you will see a significant improvement in performance. Remember - dongles are radios. They need to be in the clear to operate best.

      This coupler is a very nice, and necessary, item to have so your TV Stick can be located in the best place possible.
